errors.prescription:
1. Use safe call operator: value?.method()
2. Use safe call with let: value?.let { it.method() }
3. Use non-null assertion: value!!.method() (throws if null)
4. Use Elvis operator for default: value?.method() ?: defaultValue
5. Add a null check: if (value != null) { value.method() }

